Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Speed of Light
Formula: c = 299,792,458 m/s in vacuum
Note:    Foundation of special relativity; universal speed limit

Domain:  Geology
Topic:   Age of Earth
Formula: 4.54 billion years
Note:    Determined by radiometric dating of oldest rocks/meteorites

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Wave Equation
Formula: v = fλ
Note:    Speed of wave = frequency × wavelength

Domain:  Mathematics
